Package com.example.own_example.models

Class CampusEvent

java.lang.Object
com.example.own_example.models.CampusEvent
public class CampusEvent extends Object
Model class representing a campus event. Contains all information about an event including its details, timing, and attendance.

      id - The unique identifier for the event

      Full constructor for creating a complete event with all details.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier for the event
      title - The title of the event

      location - The location where the event will be held
      startTime - The start date and time of the event
      endTime - The end date and time of the event
      creator - The username of the event creator
      category - The category of the event (e.g., Career, Academic, Entertainment, Social)
      attendees - The number of attendees who have RSVP'd for the event
      isRsvped - Whether the current user has RSVP'd for this event
